{
  "texts": [
    "Similarly, the prompt design for the small model can impact its reasoning abilities.",
    "Additionally, our approach requires submitting questions (data) to third-party services via APIs (e.g., OpenAI), posing a risk of data leakage.",
    "Additionally, due to budget constraints, we did not utilize the most recently released GPT-4.0 as the teacher model in our experiments.",
    "We plan to explore this in future research.",
    "Shunyu Yao, Dian Yu, Jeffrey Zhao, Izhak Shafran, Thomas L Griffiths, Yuan Cao, and Karthik Narasimhan. 2023b."
  ]
}